node.text: I wanted to hop on here and express just how much I love and value you all, since I wasn’t able to give my whole thanks on stage ❤️We won Best Movie BECAUSE of you all and I wanted to express just how grateful I am to every single one of you ❤️. Thank you endlessly!

Here’s to the finale. Always and forever, Lana @toalltheboysnetflix

node.text: I am BEYOND thrilled to finally announce I am the newest face and brand ambassador for @neutrogena !!! I am thrilled to partner with Neutrogena 😍😭. I’ve waited so long to tell you all the news and I couldn’t be more excited to finally share. I have been a true fan of the brand for as long as I’ve known about skincare and it’s truly an honor to be able to work with them! Here we go! #NTGSpokesperson

Click the link in my bio to take your Smile Assessment! #invisalignpartner #invisalign #SmileSquad

node.text: June is National Acne Awareness Month so I wanted to share THE product that has been part of my clear skin arsenal and daily routine for years! @Neutrogena Oil-Free Acne Wash is a tried and true staple that combines a powerful acne treatment and cleanser in one formula (and one simple step!) to help clear and prevent breakouts. The formula contains 2% Salicylic Acid which is great for removing pore-clogging dirt and oil, as well as special skin soothers so it is gentle enough to use every day without being over-drying or irritating. #ntgspokesperson
